{"tid":538543,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人訓極都唔夠/唔識自己醒","createTime":"2018-01-23T16:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T17:36:55.000Z","uid":118011,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f27c3f5695f95de6eae3766e2c717ff3629fed7","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的 由小學開始到而家出黎做野<br />\n幾乎每朝都係唔到最後一刻唔起身<br />\n而家份工時間好彈性 唔洗早起身<br />\n但其實成日好想每朝早少少8點起身做下自己野<br />\n而最後都係10點幾11點先逼住要起身<br />\n<br />\n初頭以為自己夜訓 訓得少 又唔定時訓覺<br />\n但呢兩個月已經keep住1點訓 訓足8個鐘<br />\n可惜都係早起唔到<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁<br />\n或者有冇人幫我分析下原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37fd40b0fb447468d11a74ccfec943afece1df8","tid":538543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你放假無野做 如果任由自己訓係咪會訓到第二日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n事實上唔係個個人個睡眠時間都係8個鐘 一定有大約一個時間你會自然醒"},{"pid":"ff851d6d719da6c67ff9fe5be64c73464bf2b03d","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d37fd40b0fb447468d11a74ccfec943afece1df8","tid":538543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你放假無野做 如果任由自己訓係咪會訓到第二日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n事實上唔係個個人個睡眠時間都係8個鐘 一定有大約一個時間你會自然醒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"我中學放假冇野做嘅話 試過一覺訓15個鐘<br />\n有時訓完 起身休息再訓 可以訓19個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我平時好撚多野做<br />\n有諗過會唔會係潛意識逃避 所以唔願起<br />\n但又唔知係唔係 就算係 都唔知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272e2aeb83a3964b67588d8ebb71790ef44e8b3d","tid":538543,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"有一段時間我都曾經好想變返朝早做野，好似會精神d<br />\n但其實一起身之後跟本仲係好眼訓做唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果食埋早餐就更加<br />\n所以最後都變返夜晚做，效率仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ea61edd46c6175135cb526c7209bef121ad4e9","tid":538543,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"其實1點都係夜訓<br />\n<br />\n我要11點訓第日先會精神，雖然好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f98d3ffff1dcbe3f27e6fcf47643607b3af3ae3","tid":538543,"uid":105462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"唔<br />\n好<br />\n打<br />\n咁<br />\n多<br />\n飛<br />\n機"},{"pid":"a61a80d14a0bcd51d4e000876dfc2379943ee63c","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56ea61edd46c6175135cb526c7209bef121ad4e9","tid":538543,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"其實1點都係夜訓<br />\n<br />\n我要11點訓第日先會精神，雖然好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"咁ching幾點起身? 自然醒?"},{"pid":"4747fda3e5770cdc535492e8801ba31f8aa65676","tid":538543,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:10:06.000Z","msg":"識自己醒 但要訓夠10-12個鐘先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0f8e93b2200dbd6180fd2817c435b7935f89a9","tid":538543,"uid":11374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n星期六日 係屋企的話亦肯定會訓晏覺<br />\n幾點訓都一樣 第二朝一樣好眼訓<br />\n番工一定頂唔順恰眼訓<br />\n<br />\n明明訓親都一覺訓到大天光 點解會咁"},{"pid":"67648212c9c68f4a7a12d5e6aafaefca9dacf862","tid":538543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff851d6d719da6c67ff9fe5be64c73464bf2b03d","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d37fd40b0fb447468d11a74ccfec943afece1df8","tid":538543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你放假無野做 如果任由自己訓係咪會訓到第二日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n事實上唔係個個人個睡眠時間都係8個鐘 一定有大約一個時間你會自然醒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"我中學放假冇野做嘅話 試過一覺訓15個鐘<br />\n有時訓完 起身休息再訓 可以訓19個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我平時好撚多野做<br />\n有諗過會唔會係潛意識逃避 所以唔願起<br />\n但又唔知係唔係 就算係 都唔知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"而家幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋中學時間唔可以做比較 18歲前會特別訓到"},{"pid":"62f60fc0cc3b7fc47f1eb80f1e0caf77c9194386","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff0f8e93b2200dbd6180fd2817c435b7935f89a9","tid":538543,"uid":11374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n星期六日 係屋企的話亦肯定會訓晏覺<br />\n幾點訓都一樣 第二朝一樣好眼訓<br />\n番工一定頂唔順恰眼訓<br />\n<br />\n明明訓親都一覺訓到大天光 點解會咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"我都係要訓晏覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪個人太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb49f7a6b86a34497524d301516c6102858c643d","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67648212c9c68f4a7a12d5e6aafaefca9dacf862","tid":538543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff851d6d719da6c67ff9fe5be64c73464bf2b03d","tid":538543,"uid":118011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d37fd40b0fb447468d11a74ccfec943afece1df8","tid":538543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你放假無野做 如果任由自己訓係咪會訓到第二日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n事實上唔係個個人個睡眠時間都係8個鐘 一定有大約一個時間你會自然醒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"我中學放假冇野做嘅話 試過一覺訓15個鐘<br />\n有時訓完 起身休息再訓 可以訓19個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我平時好撚多野做<br />\n有諗過會唔會係潛意識逃避 所以唔